OL,3,CMajor Aston Villa star completes
OL,4,Ctransfer to Manchester United
OL,6,FAston Villa star Youri Tielemans has
OL,7,Fcompleted a permanent transfer to
OL,8,FManchester United.
OL,10,FTielemans joined the side in 2023 from
OL,11,FLeicester City and has made 134
OL,12,Fappearances for the Villains.
OL,14,FHe scored ten goals during his Villa
OL,15,Fcareer, but his most impactful was
OL,16,Fduring the UEFA Europa League Final,
OL,17,Fas he netted a volley that set Unai
OL,18,FEmery's side on their way to victory
OL,19,Fover Freiburg in May.
