OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784099887
OL,3,CMajor Aston Villa star completes
OL,4,Ctransfer to Manchester United
OL,6,FHe captained Belgium in the World Cup
OL,7,Fthis summer and has 90 caps for his
OL,8,Fcountry.
OL,10,FA statement from Aston Villa reads:
OL,11,F"Tielemans was a fan favourite in
OL,12,Fclaret and blue, with his stellar
OL,13,Fperformances earning him both Players'
OL,14,FPlayer and Supporters' Player of the
OL,15,FSeason awards at the end of the 2024/
OL,16,F25 campaign.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
