PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784099887
OL,3,CMajor Aston Villa star completes
OL,4,Ctransfer to Manchester United
OL,6,F"A popular and highly-respected member
OL,7,Fof the dressing room, everyone at
OL,8,FAston Villa would like to thank Youri
OL,9,Ffor his service to the club and wish
OL,10,Fhim the very best in his future
OL,11,Fcareer."
OL,13,FThe midfielder has signed a contract
OL,14,Funtil June 2031.
OL,16,FTielemans told the Manchester United
OL,17,Fclub website: "It's hard to describe
OL,18,Fjust how proud I am to join Manchester
OL,19,FUnited.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
