OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784099887
OL,3,CMajor Aston Villa star completes
OL,4,Ctransfer to Manchester United
OL,6,F"Signing for such a special club feels
OL,7,Fincredible, it is the culmination of
OL,8,Fyears of dedication since I first fell
OL,9,Fin love with football.
OL,11,F"I have had the privilege of
OL,12,Fexperiencing success in the game and
OL,13,Fit has only increased my determination
OL,14,Fto achieve more.
OL,16,F"The ambition from everyone at the
OL,17,Fclub is extremely clear, we are all
OL,18,Fdetermined to push for the biggest
OL,19,Ftrophies over the coming years."
